<h3 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_LWe7" id="2-the-feynman-learning-technique">2. The Feynman Learning Technique<a href="https://dheerajinampudi.com/blog/mental-models#2-the-feynman-learning-technique" class="hash-link" aria-label="Direct link to 2. The Feynman Learning Technique" title="Direct link to 2. The Feynman Learning Technique">​</a></h3>
