</ul>
<h3 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_LWe7" id="3-understanding-your-circle-of-competence">3. Understanding Your Circle of Competence<a href="https://dheerajinampudi.com/blog/mental-models#3-understanding-your-circle-of-competence" class="hash-link" aria-label="Direct link to 3. Understanding Your Circle of Competence" title="Direct link to 3. Understanding Your Circle of Competence">​</a></h3>
